
The standard library {\tt Threadkit\_Io\_Cleanup\_At\_Shutdown} api defines tracking of open I/O streams, to close them cleanly at exit.

The {\tt Threadkit\_Io\_Cleanup\_At\_Shutdown} api is implemented by the \ahrefloc{pkg:threadkit\_io\_cleanup\_at\_shutdown}{io\_cleanup\_at\_shutdown} package.

The {\tt Io\_Cleanup\_At\_Shutodwn} api source code is in \ahrefloc{src/lib/std/src/io/io-cleanup-at-shutdown.api}{src/lib/std/src/io/io-cleanup-at-shutdown.api}.

See also: \ahrefloc{api:Io\_Cleanup\_At\_Shutdown}{Io\_Cleanup\_At\_Shutdown}.




